cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for person recognition in personal photo collections. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses related work and the state of the art, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the security implications of person recognition, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
